  <brief_title>Reduction of Catheter-associated Urinary Tract Infection With a Daily Nursing Review of the Indication</brief_title>
  <official_title>Reduction of Catheter-associated Urinary Tract Infection With a Daily Nursing Review of the Indication. Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
